---
title: troy. is a band
description: I make music under the name troy. See, it's easy to remember because it is actually my name. Anyway, I hope you like it.
plvylist: true
layout: main
---
<main>
  <section id="about">
    <div class="wrapper">
      <h1>this is a band.</h1>
      <div class="flex flex-middle space-out center">
        <img src="/assets/img/aiacr.jpg" alt="Album art for Alone in a Crowded Room">
        <p><i>(This is an album)</i></p>
      </div>
      <div class="btn">
        <a href="https://distrokid.com/hyperfollow/actionhamilton/bFzI" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Listen/Stream</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section id="stream">
    <div class="heading">
      <div class="wrapper">
        <h2>you can also stream here.</h2>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="plvylist"></div>
  </section>
  <section id="demos">
    <div class="heading">
      <div class="wrapper">
        <h2>unreleased footage alert!</h2>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="wrapper">
      <p>Find demos and more behind the scenes footage in the demos vault.</p>
      {% for demo in demos.aloneDemos.slice(0, 2) %}
      <div class="grid two-col">
        <video controls playsinline>
          <source src="{{ demo.srcH264 }}" type="video/mp4">
          Sorry, your browser doesn't support these videos!
        </video>
        <p>{{ demo.file }}</p>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
      <div>
        <a href="/demos">Demo Vault</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>
